            <p>Os <span xlink:href="urn:lex:br:federal:constituicao:1988-10-05;1988!art7">arts. 7º</span>, <span xlink:href="urn:lex:br:federal:constituicao:1988-10-05;1988!art23">23</span>, <span xlink:href="urn:lex:br:federal:constituicao:1988-10-05;1988!art24">24</span>, <span xlink:href="urn:lex:br:federal:constituicao:1988-10-05;1988!art37">37</span>, <span xlink:href="urn:lex:br:federal:constituicao:1988-10-05;1988!art40">40</span>, <span xlink:href="urn:lex:br:federal:constituicao:1988-10-05;1988!art201">201</span>, <span xlink:href="urn:lex:br:federal:constituicao:1988-10-05;1988!art203">203</span>, <span xlink:href="urn:lex:br:federal:constituicao:1988-10-05;1988!art208">208</span>, <span xlink:href="urn:lex:br:federal:constituicao:1988-10-05;1988!art227">227</span> e <span xlink:href="urn:lex:br:federal:constituicao:1988-10-05;1988!art244">244 da Constituição Federal</span> passam a vigorar com as seguintes alterações:</p>
